avahi: avahi (Local network service discovery)
avahi:
avahi: Avahi is a system which facilitates service discovery on local
avahi: network -- this means that you can plug your laptop or computer
avahi: into a network and instantly be able to view other people who
avahi: you can chat with, find printers to print to or find files being
avahi: shared.
avahi:
avahi: http://avahi.org
